277|
<!-- CRYPTOGRAPHY -->
<div class="section" id="sec-crypto">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">🔒</span>
    <div>
      <div class="section-title">Cryptography</div>
      <div class="section-desc">เครื่องมือถอด/วิเคราะห์รหัส — classical ciphers, RSA, hash cracking</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="subsection">
    <div class="subsection-title">🛠 Tools</div>
    <div class="tool-grid">

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">dCode</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.dcode.fr" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">สวรรค์ของ cryptography — รวมตัวถอดรหัสมากกว่า 200+ cipher ทั้ง Caesar, Vigenere, Base*, Rail Fence, Playfair, Bacon, Polybius ฯลฯ มี cipher identifier ด้วย</div>
        <div class="tip">💡 ถ้าไม่รู้ว่าเป็น cipher อะไร ให้ลอง <strong>Cipher Identifier</strong> ที่ dCode ก่อนเสมอ</div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">RsaCtfTool</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/Ganapati/RsaCtfTool" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">เครื่องมือโจมตี RSA อัตโนมัติ รองรับ attacks หลายรูปแบบ: factordb, wiener, small_e, common modulus, hastad, LSB oracle ฯลฯ</div>
        <div class="tool-usage">
          <div class="tool-usage-label">ติดตั้ง &amp; ใช้งาน</div>
          <pre>git clone https://github.com/Ganapati/RsaCtfTool
cd RsaCtfTool && pip3 install -r requirements.txt

# จากไฟล์ public key + ciphertext
python3 RsaCtfTool.py --publickey pub.pem --uncipherfile cipher.enc

# ระบุ n, e โดยตรง
python3 RsaCtfTool.py --n 1234567890... --e 65537 --uncipher 9876543210...

# ลองทุก attack
python3 RsaCtfTool.py --publickey pub.pem --attack all</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">FactorDB</span><a class="tool-link" href="http://factordb.com/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">ฐานข้อมูล integer factorization ถ้า n ของ RSA เคยถูก factor มาก่อน จะพบที่นี่ทันที</div>
        <div class="tool-usage">
          <div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้ใน Python</div>
          <pre>from factordb.factordb import FactorDB
f = FactorDB(n)
f.connect()
print(f.get_factor_list())  # [p, q]</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">CrackStation</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://crackstation.net/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">ถอด hash ออนไลน์ฟรี รองรับ MD5, SHA-1, SHA-224, SHA-256, SHA-384, SHA-512 มี rainbow table ขนาดใหญ่มาก</div>
        <div class="tool-usage">
          <div class="tool-usage-label">หรือใช้ hashcat</div>
          <pre># MD5
hashcat -m 0 hash.txt /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt
# SHA-256
hashcat -m 1400 hash.txt rockyou.txt
# bcrypt
hashcat -m 3200 hash.txt rockyou.txt</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">QuipQiup</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://quipqiup.com/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Substitution cipher solver แบบอัตโนมัติ ใช้ frequency analysis ไม่ต้องรู้ key รองรับการใส่ hint เพิ่มเติม</div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Vigenere Solver</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.guballa.de/vigenere-solver" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">ถอด Vigenere cipher แบบ brute-force หาความยาว key อัตโนมัติ</div>
        <div class="tool-usage">
          <div class="tool-usage-label">หรือใช้ Python</div>
          <pre>from pycipher import Vigenere
Vigenere('KEY').decipher('CIPHERTEXT')

# Kasiski + Index of Coincidence test (ใช้ lib: pycryptodome)
</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">RSA Step-by-Step</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.cryptool.org/en/cto/highlights/rsa-step-by-step" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Calculator แสดง RSA ทีละ step: key generation, encryption, decryption รองรับตัวเลขขนาดใหญ่</div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">SageMath Online</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://sagecell.sagemath.org/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Sage environment ออนไลน์สำหรับคำนวณ crypto — modular arithmetic, polynomial factoring, elliptic curves</div>
        <div class="tool-usage">
          <div class="tool-usage-label">ตัวอย่าง RSA decryption ใน Sage</div>
          <pre>p = 61; q = 53; e = 17
n = p*q
phi = (p-1)*(q-1)
d = inverse_mod(e, phi)
# decrypt: m = pow(c, d, n)
m = pow(2790, d, n)
print(m)</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Morse Code Translator</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://morsecode.world/international/translator.html" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">แปลง text ↔ Morse code ทั้งแบบ text และ audio</div>
        <div class="tool-usage">
          <div class="tool-usage-label">Python quick decode</div>
          <pre>MORSE = {'.-':'A','-.':'B','-.-. ':'C',...}
# หรือ pip install morse-talk
import morse
morse.decode('.... . .-.. .-.. ---')</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">DTMF Dual Tone Decoder</span><a class="tool-link" href="http://dialabc.com/sound/detect/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">วิเคราะห์ DTMF tones จาก audio file — เสียง dial ของโทรศัพท์ที่อาจซ่อน flag ไว้</div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Hash Identifier</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://tools.kali.org/password-attacks/hash-identifier" target="_blank">🔗 Kali</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">ระบุประเภทของ hash จาก pattern</div>
        <div class="tool-usage">
          <div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน (Kali)</div>
          <pre>hash-identifier
# หรือใช้ hashid:
pip3 install hashid
hashid 5d41402abc4b2a76b9719d911017c592</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">gmpy2</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://gmpy2.readthedocs.io/" target="_blank">🔗 Docs</a></div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Python library สำหรับ big number arithmetic ใช้งานใน RSA CTF challenges บ่อยมาก</div>
        <div class="tool-usage">
          <div class="tool-usage-label">ตัวอย่าง</div>
          <pre>import gmpy2
# modular inverse
d = int(gmpy2.invert(e, phi))
# integer sqrt
root, exact = gmpy2.iroot(n, 2)  # sqrt(n)
# power mod
m = int(gmpy2.powmod(c, d, n))</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
      </div>

    </div><!-- tool-grid -->
  </div><!-- subsection tools -->

  <div class="subsection">
    <div class="subsection-title">📚 Common CTF Crypto Patterns</div>
    <div class="tool-grid">
      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-name" style="margin-bottom:8px">RSA Attack Checklist</div>
        <pre>1. Small e (e=3) + small m  → cube root attack
2. Small d (Wiener)         → RsaCtfTool --attack wiener
3. n=p*q ที่ p≈q (smooth)  → Fermat factorization
4. Common modulus           → gcd(n1,n2) != 1
5. e=1                      → m = c
6. p,q จาก FactorDB        → ตรงๆ เลย
7. Hastad (same m, multiple n) → CRT + cube root</pre>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-name" style="margin-bottom:8px">Classic Cipher Quick ID</div>
        <pre>Only A-Z uppercase, no spaces → Caesar / Vigenere
Numbers only (1-26)           → A1Z26
Dots and dashes               → Morse
+ . symbols                   → Tap code / Braille
Symbol substitution           → dCode Symbolic Ciphers
Bacon's cipher                → A/B or 0/1 sequences
Polybius square               → 2-digit numbers 1-5</pre>
        <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div><!-- /sec-crypto -->

<!-- STEGANOGRAPHY -->
<div class="section" id="sec-stego">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">🎨</span>
    <div>
      <div class="section-title">Steganography</div>
      <div class="section-desc">ค้นหาและสกัดข้อมูลซ่อนในรูปภาพ, เสียง, วิดีโอ</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-grid">

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Aperi'Solve</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://aperisolve.fr/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">One-stop stego analysis — อัปโหลดรูปแล้วรัน zsteg, steghide, exiftool, binwalk, foremost, strings ให้ครบใน click เดียว</div>
      <div class="tip">💡 เริ่ม stego ด้วย Aperi'Solve ก่อนเสมอ — ประหยัดเวลามาก</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">StegOnline</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://stegonline.georgeom.net" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ดู bit planes ของรูปภาพ แยก LSB ทีละ bit ดู color channels แยก extract embedded data</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Stegsolve</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/eugenekolo/sec-tools/tree/master/stego/stegsolve/stegsolve" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Java GUI tool สำหรับ bit plane analysis, XOR/AND/OR combine สองภาพ, color filter ดู hidden text</div>
      <div class="tool-usage">
        <div class="tool-usage-label">รัน</div>
        <pre>java -jar stegsolve.jar</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-java">Java</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">steghide</span><a class="tool-link" href="http://steghide.sourceforge.net/documentation/manpage.php" target="_blank">🔗 Docs</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ฝัง/สกัดข้อมูลใน JPEG, BMP, WAV, AU — มักใช้กับ password</div>
      <div class="tool-usage">
        <div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
        <pre># สกัดข้อมูล (ไม่มี password)
steghide extract -sf image.jpg -p ""
# ด้วย password
steghide extract -sf image.jpg -p mysecret
# ดู info
steghide info image.jpg</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Stegseek</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/RickdeJager/stegseek" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">steghide cracker ความเร็วสูง brute-force password ของ steghide ด้วย wordlist ได้เร็วมาก</div>
      <div class="tool-usage">
        <div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
        <pre>stegseek image.jpg /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt
# ถ้า password ว่าง:
stegseek --crack image.jpg wordlist.txt</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">zsteg</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/zed-0xff/zsteg" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ตรวจหา steganography ใน PNG และ BMP — LSB, MSB, bit planes, text, zlib hidden data</div>
      <div class="tool-usage">
        <div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
        <pre>gem install zsteg
zsteg image.png           # scan ทุก channel
zsteg -a image.png        # scan ทุก combination
zsteg -E "b1,rgb,lsb,xy" image.png  # extract specific</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-ruby">Ruby</span><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">binwalk</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/ReFirmLabs/binwalk" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ค้นหา embedded files/data ภายในไฟล์ binary โดยดู magic bytes — พบไฟล์ซ่อนในรูปได้บ่อยมาก</div>
      <div class="tool-usage">
        <div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
        <pre>binwalk image.png               # scan
binwalk -e image.png            # extract
binwalk -dd '.*' image.png      # extract everything
binwalk --dd 'zip archive' file # extract zip เท่านั้น</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">exiftool</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://exiftool.org/" target="_blank">🔗 Docs</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">อ่าน/แก้ metadata ของไฟล์ image, audio, video — flag มักซ่อนอยู่ใน comment หรือ EXIF fields</div>
      <div class="tool-usage">
        <div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
        <pre>exiftool image.jpg          # ดู metadata ทั้งหมด
exiftool -Comment image.jpg # ดูเฉพาะ comment
exiftool -all= image.jpg    # ลบ metadata ทั้งหมด</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="subsection" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="subsection-title">📌 Stego Checklist</div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <pre>1. exiftool / strings  → ดู metadata + printable strings
2. Aperi'Solve         → one-click analysis (zsteg + steghide + binwalk)
3. hexdump / xxd       → ดู magic bytes, file trailer
4. binwalk -e          → extract embedded files
5. zsteg -a            → LSB/MSB bit planes (PNG/BMP)
6. steghide extract    → password-based embed (JPEG/WAV)
7. stegseek            → brute-force steghide password
8. Stegsolve           → bit plane viewer, combine images
9. strings -n 6        → ค้นหา strings ยาว
10. foremost           → data carving จาก binary stream</pre>
    </div>
  </div>

</div><!-- /sec-stego -->

<!-- WEB -->
<div class="section" id="sec-web">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">🕸️</span>
    <div><div class="section-title">Web Exploitation</div>
    <div class="section-desc">SQLi, XSS, LFI, SSRF, CSP bypass และเทคนิค web hacking</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">PayloadsAllTheThings</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/swisskyrepo/PayloadsAllTheThings" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">รวม payloads ทุกเทคนิค web hacking — SQLi, XSS, SSRF, LFI, RCE, XXE, SSTI อ้างอิง first เสมอ</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">LFI Payloads</div>
<pre>../../../../etc/passwd
....//....//etc/passwd
php://filter/convert.base64-encode/resource=/etc/passwd
data://text/plain;base64,PD9waHAgc3lzdGVtKCRfR0VUWydjbWQnXSk7Pz4=</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">CSP Evaluator</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://csp-evaluator.withgoogle.com/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">วิเคราะห์ Content Security Policy header บอก weakness และ bypass possibilities</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">SQLMap</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://sqlmap.org/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Automatic SQL injection detection/exploitation — MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQLite, MSSQL</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
<pre>sqlmap -u "http://target/?id=1" --dbs
sqlmap -u "http://target/" --data="u=a&p=b" --dbs
sqlmap -r request.txt --level=5 --risk=3
sqlmap -u "..." -D db -T users --dump</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Burp Suite</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://portswigger.net/burp" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Web proxy intercept/modify HTTP — Repeater (manual test), Intruder (brute-force), Decoder</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Tips</div>
<pre>Ctrl+R → send to Repeater
Ctrl+I → send to Intruder
Decoder tab: URL / HTML / Base64 / Hex</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-java">Java</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Subdomain Finder</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://subdomainfinder.c99.nl/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ค้นหา subdomain ที่ซ่อนอยู่รวมถึง wildcard และ dev/staging subdomains</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">CLI</div>
<pre>subfinder -d example.com
gobuster dns -d example.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dns.txt</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">JSONP Endpoints</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/zigoo0/JSONBee/blob/master/jsonp.txt" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">รายการ JSONP endpoints ที่รู้จัก ใช้ bypass CSP ที่ whitelist domain เหล่านั้น</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Google Certificate Transparency</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://transparencyreport.google.com/https/certificates" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ค้น SSL certificates ของ domain ช่วยหา subdomain ที่ไม่เปิดเผย</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="subsection" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="subsection-title">📌 Web CTF Checklist</div>
    <div class="tool-card"><pre>1. robots.txt / /.git/ / /.env    → info leak
2. View source + JS files          → hardcoded keys
3. Cookie + jwt.io                 → tamper JWT
4. SQLi: ' OR 1=1--                → sqlmap -r req.txt
5. LFI: ../../../../etc/passwd     → php://filter
6. SSTI: {{7*7}} / ${7*7}          → template injection
7. SSRF: param รับ URL            → scan internal
8. XXE / Command injection         → PayloadsAllTheThings</pre></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PWN -->
<div class="section" id="sec-pwn">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">🐛</span>
    <div><div class="section-title">Pwn / Binary Exploitation</div>
    <div class="section-desc">Buffer overflow, ROP chains, shellcode, binary analysis</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">pwntools</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://docs.pwntools.com/" target="_blank">🔗 Docs</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Python library มาตรฐาน CTF pwn — process/remote, ROP chains, shellcraft, ELF parsing, format string</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Template พื้นฐาน</div>
<pre>from pwn import *
context.arch = 'amd64'
p = process('./vuln')          # local
p = remote('chall.ctf.com', 9001)
elf = ELF('./vuln')
rop = ROP(elf)
rop.raw(rop.ret)               # stack alignment
rop.call(elf.plt['puts'], [elf.got['puts']])
p.sendline(flat({offset: rop.chain()}))
p.interactive()</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">DogBolt / Decompiler Explorer</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://dogbolt.org/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Decompile binary ออนไลน์พร้อมกันด้วย Ghidra, BinaryNinja, angr, RetDec — เปรียบเทียบหลาย decompiler</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Syscall Reference</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://syscalls.w3challs.com/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ตาราง Linux syscalls x86/x64 พร้อมค่า registers — ใช้เขียน shellcode</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">x64 execve shellcode</div>
<pre># rax=59, rdi=ptr"/bin/sh", rsi=0, rdx=0
from pwn import *
context.arch='amd64'
print(enhex(asm(shellcraft.sh())))</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">LibC Database</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://libc.blukat.me/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">หา libc version จาก leaked address ของ function — ใช้ใน ret2libc attacks</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Workflow</div>
<pre># 1. leak puts@got → ใส่ใน libc.blukat.me
# 2. คำนวณ offset:
from pwn import *
libc = ELF('libc.so.6')
sys = leaked_puts - libc.sym['puts'] + libc.sym['system']
binsh = leaked_puts - libc.sym['puts'] + next(libc.search(b'/bin/sh'))</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">x86/x64 Online Assembler</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://defuse.ca/online-x86-assembler.htm" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">แปลง assembly ↔ hex bytes ออนไลน์ รองรับ x86 และ x64</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">BinaryNinja Cloud</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://cloud.binary.ninja/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Binary decompiler ออนไลน์ — Control Flow Graph, decompiled C, function list</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="subsection" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="subsection-title">📌 Pwn Checklist</div>
    <div class="tool-card"><pre>1. checksec --file=./vuln     → NX/PIE/RELRO/Canary
2. file ./vuln               → 32/64-bit, stripped?
3. strings ./vuln            → hardcoded passwords/flags
4. ltrace / strace ./vuln    → library/syscall trace
5. gdb + pwndbg              → pattern create 200 → find offset
6. ROPgadget --binary ./vuln → find ROP gadgets
7. DogBolt / Ghidra          → decompile main logic
8. No NX → shellcode | NX+no PIE → ret2plt/ret2libc</pre></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FORENSICS -->
<div class="section" id="sec-forensics">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">🕵️</span>
    <div><div class="section-title">Forensics</div>
    <div class="section-desc">File carving, memory forensics, disk imaging, metadata analysis</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Forensically</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://29a.ch/photo-forensics/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Online forensic analysis — Error Level Analysis (ELA), noise analysis, luminance gradient, clone detection สำหรับตรวจรูปที่ถูกแก้ไข</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Autopsy</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.sleuthkit.org/autopsy/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">GUI forensic tool สำหรับวิเคราะห์ disk image — file recovery, timeline, keyword search, browser history</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">foremost</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://tools.kali.org/forensics/foremost" target="_blank">🔗 Kali</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Data carving จาก disk image หรือ binary file โดยค้นหา magic bytes ของ JPEG, PNG, ZIP, PDF ฯลฯ</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
<pre>foremost -i image.raw -o output/
foremost -t jpg,png,zip -i file.bin -o out/
# ดูผล
ls out/audit.txt</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Volatility</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.volatilityfoundation.org/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Memory forensics framework — วิเคราะห์ RAM dump: processes, network connections, registry, passwords, injected code</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน (vol3)</div>
<pre>vol -f mem.dmp windows.info
vol -f mem.dmp windows.pslist
vol -f mem.dmp windows.netscan
vol -f mem.dmp windows.cmdline
vol -f mem.dmp windows.filescan | grep flag
vol -f mem.dmp windows.dumpfiles --virtaddr 0x...</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Wireshark / tshark</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.wireshark.org/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">วิเคราะห์ PCAP network traffic — ดู HTTP/DNS/FTP/SMTP protocol, export files, follow TCP stream</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">tshark one-liners</div>
<pre>tshark -r capture.pcap -Y "http" -T fields -e http.request.uri
tshark -r capture.pcap --export-objects http,out/
tshark -r capture.pcap -z io,phs -q   # protocol stats
tshark -r capture.pcap -Y "dns" -T fields -e dns.qry.name</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">strings + xxd + binwalk</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/ReFirmLabs/binwalk" target="_blank">🔗 binwalk</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">เครื่องมือพื้นฐาน — strings ค้น printable text, xxd dump hex, binwalk scan/extract embedded files</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
<pre>strings -n 8 file.bin | grep -i flag
xxd file.bin | head -50
xxd -r hexdump.txt > output.bin   # reverse hex
binwalk -e file.bin               # extract embedded
file file.bin                     # identify type</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="subsection" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="subsection-title">📌 Forensics Checklist</div>
    <div class="tool-card"><pre>1. file / xxd / strings       → ระบุประเภทและค้น text
2. exiftool                   → metadata / EXIF
3. binwalk -e                 → embedded files
4. foremost / photorec        → file carving
5. Wireshark → Follow Stream  → HTTP/FTP plaintext
6. Volatility (RAM dump)      → processes, network, files
7. Autopsy (disk image)       → timeline, deleted files
8. strings -a -e l file.bin   → Unicode strings (Windows)</pre></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- OSINT -->
<div class="section" id="sec-osint">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">🌐</span>
    <div><div class="section-title">OSINT</div>
    <div class="section-desc">Open Source Intelligence — ค้นหาข้อมูลจากแหล่งสาธารณะ</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Wayback Machine</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://archive.org/web/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ดู snapshot ของเว็บไซต์ในอดีต — ค้นหา version เก่าที่อาจเปิดเผยข้อมูล, source code, หรือ credentials</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">ค้นหาผ่าน API</div>
<pre>curl "http://archive.org/wayback/available?url=example.com"
# ดู snapshots ทั้งหมด:
curl "http://web.archive.org/cdx/search/cdx?url=example.com/*&output=list"</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Sherlock</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/sherlock-project/sherlock" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ค้นหา social media accounts จาก username เดียวกันทั่วทุกแพลตฟอร์ม</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
<pre>pip3 install sherlock-project
sherlock username
sherlock --timeout 5 --print-found username</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Epieos</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://epieos.com/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ค้นหาข้อมูลที่เชื่อมกับ email address — Google account, social media, data breach</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">LinkedIn Email Finder</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://skrapp.io/tutorials/linkedin-email-finder" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Chrome extension หา email จาก LinkedIn profile</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Google Dorks</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.exploit-db.com/google-hacking-database" target="_blank">🔗 GHDB</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ค้นหาข้อมูลสำคัญผ่าน Google search operators</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Useful dorks</div>
<pre>site:example.com filetype:pdf
site:example.com inurl:admin
intitle:"index of" "password"
intext:"api_key" site:github.com
site:pastebin.com "example.com" password</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">ExifTool (OSINT)</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://exiftool.org/" target="_blank">🔗 Docs</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">ดู GPS coordinates จากรูปภาพ — latitude/longitude ซ่อนอยู่ใน EXIF</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">ดู GPS</div>
<pre>exiftool -GPS* image.jpg
exiftool -n -GPSLatitude -GPSLongitude image.jpg
# แล้วนำค่าไปค้นใน Google Maps</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- REVERSING -->
<div class="section" id="sec-reversing">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">↩️</span>
    <div><div class="section-title">Reverse Engineering</div>
    <div class="section-desc">Decompile, disassemble, analyze executables และ APKs</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Ghidra</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://ghidra-sre.org/" target="_blank">🔗 Download</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Free reverse engineering tool จาก NSA — decompile ไปเป็น C-like code, ดู disassembly, function analysis, cross-references</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Tips</div>
<pre># ค้นหา strings ใน Defined Strings window
# ใช้ Ctrl+F ค้น function
# ดู xrefs ด้วย Ctrl+Shift+F
# Script: Find flag patterns:
import re
memory = getCurrentProgram().getMemory()
# ใช้ Search > Memory สำหรับค้น bytes</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-java">Java</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">DogBolt</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://dogbolt.org/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Upload binary → decompile พร้อมกันด้วย Ghidra, BinaryNinja, angr, Hex-Rays — เลือกผลที่อ่านง่ายที่สุด</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">JADX (Android)</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/skylot/jadx" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Decompile APK → Java source code — ดู classes, string constants, AndroidManifest, ค้น API keys ที่ hardcode</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">ใช้งาน</div>
<pre>jadx -d output/ app.apk
jadx-gui app.apk          # GUI mode
# ค้นหา:
grep -r "flag\|password\|secret\|api_key" output/</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-java">Java</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Online Java Decompiler</span><a class="tool-link" href="http://www.javadecompilers.com/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Decompile Java .class, .jar, APK ออนไลน์ — ไม่ต้องติดตั้งอะไร</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">pyinstxtractor</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/extremecoders-re/pyinstxtractor" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Extract Python bytecode จาก PyInstaller executable (.exe) แล้วใช้ uncompyle6/pycdc decompile กลับเป็น .py</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Workflow</div>
<pre>python3 pyinstxtractor.py chall.exe
# output: chall.exe_extracted/
# หา .pyc ที่ชื่อเหมือน exe
cd chall.exe_extracted/
uncompyle6 chall.pyc > chall.py
# หรือใช้ pycdc:
pycdc chall.pyc</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">MobSF</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://github.com/MobSF/Mobile-Security-Framework-MobSF" target="_blank">🔗 GitHub</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Automated APK/IPA security analysis — decompile, static analysis, secret scanning, permission analysis</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Run with Docker</div>
<pre>docker run -it -p 8000:8000 opensecurity/mobile-security-framework-mobsf
# เปิด http://localhost:8000 แล้ว upload APK</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="subsection" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="subsection-title">📌 Reversing Checklist</div>
    <div class="tool-card"><pre>1. file / strings            → ระบุประเภท, ค้น hardcoded
2. ltrace / strace           → trace function calls
3. Ghidra / DogBolt          → decompile logic
4. gdb + ni/si               → step through instructions
5. Python exe: pyinstxtractor → uncompyle6/pycdc
6. APK: jadx / MobSF         → Java source + manifest
7. .NET: ILSpy / dotPeek     → C# source code
8. upx -d binary             → unpack UPX packed binary</pre></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- NETWORK -->
<div class="section" id="sec-network">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">📡</span>
    <div><div class="section-title">Network Forensics</div>
    <div class="section-desc">PCAP analysis, protocol dissection, traffic reconstruction</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Wireshark</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.wireshark.org/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">GUI packet analyzer — filter, follow streams, export objects (HTTP/FTP/SMB), decode protocols</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Display Filters ที่ใช้บ่อย</div>
<pre>http                          # HTTP traffic ทั้งหมด
http.request.method == "POST" # POST requests
tcp.stream eq 0               # TCP stream แรก
dns                           # DNS queries
ftp-data                      # FTP file transfers
frame contains "flag"         # ค้น keyword ใน packets
ip.src == 192.168.1.1         # source IP</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">tshark</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.wireshark.org/docs/man-pages/tshark.html" target="_blank">🔗 Docs</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">CLI version ของ Wireshark — batch analysis, extract fields, export objects</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">One-liners</div>
<pre># ดู HTTP URIs
tshark -r cap.pcap -Y http -T fields -e http.request.uri
# export HTTP objects
tshark -r cap.pcap --export-objects http,./out/
# ดู DNS queries
tshark -r cap.pcap -Y dns -T fields -e dns.qry.name
# ดู credentials (FTP/HTTP Basic)
tshark -r cap.pcap -Y ftp -T fields -e ftp.request.command -e ftp.request.arg
# TCP stream เป็น text
tshark -r cap.pcap -q -z follow,tcp,ascii,0</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">NetworkMiner</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://www.netresec.com/?page=NetworkMiner" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Passive network sniffer/analyzer ที่ดีมาก — auto-extract files จาก PCAP, ดู sessions, credentials, DNS</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Scapy</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://scapy.net/" target="_blank">🔗 Docs</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Python library สร้าง/parse/send packets — ใช้วิเคราะห์ PCAP, craft custom packets, implement protocols</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Parse PCAP</div>
<pre>from scapy.all import *
pkts = rdpcap('capture.pcap')
for pkt in pkts:
    if pkt.haslayer(Raw):
        print(pkt[Raw].load)
    if pkt.haslayer(DNS):
        print(pkt[DNS].qd.qname)</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">nmap</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://nmap.org/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Network scanner — ค้นหา open ports, services, OS detection, vulnerability scripts</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Common scans</div>
<pre>nmap -sV -sC -p- target.com     # full scan + scripts
nmap -sV --script vuln target   # vuln scan
nmap -p 80,443,8080 target      # specific ports
nmap -A -T4 192.168.1.0/24      # aggressive subnet</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MISC -->
<div class="section" id="sec-misc">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-icon">🔧</span>
    <div><div class="section-title">Misc &amp; General Tips</div>
    <div class="section-desc">เทคนิค, one-liners, และเครื่องมือที่ใช้ข้ามหลาย category</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Base Encodings Cheatsheet</span></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Encoding ที่เจอบ่อยใน CTF</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Python decode all</div>
<pre>import base64, binascii
s = "SGVsbG8="
base64.b64decode(s)                    # Base64
base64.b32decode(s)                    # Base32
base64.b16decode(s)                    # Base16 (Hex)
base64.b85decode(s)                    # Base85
bytes.fromhex("48656c6c6f")            # Hex
binascii.a2b_uu(s)                     # UUencoding
# ลอง CyberChef "Magic" recipe อัตโนมัติ</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Flag Format Quick Reference</span></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Format ของ flag ที่ใช้บ่อยในแต่ละ CTF</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Patterns</div>
<pre>picoCTF{...}     HTB{...}       CTF{...}
flag{...}        FLAG{...}      DUCTF{...}
# MD5-style: 32 hex chars = d8e8fca2dc0f896fd7cb4cb0031ba249
# grep ค้นหา:
grep -rP "(flag|ctf|picoCTF)\{[^}]+\}" .
strings file | grep -iP "flag|ctf{|\w{32}"</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Python Crypto Snippets</span></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">One-liners ที่ใช้บ่อยมากใน CTF</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Common operations</div>
<pre># bytes ↔ int
n = int.from_bytes(b'flag', 'big')
b = n.to_bytes((n.bit_length()+7)//8, 'big')

# XOR bruteforce single byte
ct = bytes.fromhex("1b3b2b")
for k in range(256):
    pt = bytes([b^k for b in ct])
    if pt.isascii(): print(k, pt)

# Modular inverse
from math import gcd
def modinv(a, m):
    g, x, _ = extended_gcd(a, m)
    return x % m

# ROT bruteforce
for i in range(26):
    print(i, ''.join(chr((ord(c)-65+i)%26+65) if c.isupper() else c for c in ciphertext))</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Linux Privilege Escalation</span></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">เทคนิค privesc ที่เจอบ่อยใน CTF</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Quick checks</div>
<pre>sudo -l                      # sudo permissions
find / -perm -4000 2>/dev/null  # SUID binaries
cat /etc/crontab             # cron jobs
env                          # environment variables
cat /etc/passwd              # users
ss -tlnp                     # listening services
# GTFOBins: https://gtfobins.github.io/
# ค้น SUID binary ที่สามารถ abuse ได้</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">GTFOBins</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://gtfobins.github.io/" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">รายการ Unix binaries ที่ใช้ bypass security restrictions ได้ — sudo, SUID, capabilities, file write/read, shell escape</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">john + hashcat</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://hashcat.net/hashcat/" target="_blank">🔗 hashcat</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">Password cracking — john สำหรับ format หลากหลาย, hashcat สำหรับ GPU-accelerated cracking</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Common commands</div>
<pre># john
john --wordlist=rockyou.txt hash.txt
john --format=md5 hash.txt
zip2john/ssh2john/pdf2john → hash.txt
# hashcat
hashcat -m 0    hash.txt rockyou.txt  # MD5
hashcat -m 1000 hash.txt rockyou.txt  # NTLM
hashcat -m 1800 hash.txt rockyou.txt  # sha512crypt
hashcat -m 3200 hash.txt rockyou.txt  # bcrypt</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">CyberChef Magic</span><a class="tool-link" href="https://gchq.github.io/CyberChef/#recipe=Magic(3,false,false,'')" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">CyberChef "Magic" operation — ลอง decode/decrypt อัตโนมัติหลาย layer พร้อมกัน ใส่ ciphertext แล้วให้มัน detect เอง</div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-online">Online</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">Audio Stego (WAV/MP3)</span></div>
      <div class="tool-desc">เทคนิคซ่อนข้อมูลในไฟล์เสียง</div>
      <div class="tool-usage"><div class="tool-usage-label">Tools &amp; techniques</div>
<pre># Spectrogram analysis (ดู hidden image ใน spectrum):
sox audio.wav -n spectrogram -o spec.png
# หรือใช้ Sonic Visualiser / Audacity
# LSB audio stego:
python3 -c "
import wave, struct
w = wave.open('audio.wav')
frames = w.readframes(w.getnframes())
samples = struct.unpack('<'+'h'*w.getnframes(), frames)
lsbs = ''.join(str(s&1) for s in samples[:100])
print(lsbs)
"
# DTMF decoder: http://dialabc.com/sound/detect/</pre></div>
      <div class="tool-tags"><span class="tag tag-python">Python</span><span class="tag tag-cli">CLI</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


</div><!-- end all-sections -->

<div id="search-results">
  <div class="page-header"><h2>🔍 ผลการค้นหา</h2><p id="search-count"></p></div>
  <div id="search-list"></div>
</div>

</main>
</div><!-- #app -->
<button id="back-top" onclick="window.scrollTo({top:0,behavior:'smooth'})">↑</button>

<script>
const TOOL_DATA=[];
document.querySelectorAll('.tool-card').forEach(card=>{
  const sec=card.closest('.section');
  TOOL_DATA.push({
    name:card.querySelector('.tool-name')?.textContent||'',
    desc:card.querySelector('.tool-desc')?.textContent||'',
    usage:card.querySelector('.tool-usage')?.textContent||'',
    secTitle:sec?.querySelector('.section-title')?.textContent||'',
    link:card.querySelector('.tool-link')?.href||'',
    el:card
  });
});

function showSection(id){
  document.getElementById('all-sections').style.display='';
  document.getElementById('search-results').style.display='none';
  document.getElementById('search-box').value='';
  document.querySelectorAll('.nav-item').forEach(b=>{
    b.classList.toggle('active', b.getAttribute('onclick')===`showSection('${id}')`);
  });
  if(id==='all'){
    document.querySelectorAll('.section').forEach(s=>s.style.display='');
  } else {
    document.querySelectorAll('.section').forEach(s=>{
      s.style.display = s.id==='sec-'+id ? '' : 'none';
    });
  }
  window.scrollTo({top:0,behavior:'smooth'});
}

const sb=document.getElementById('search-box');
sb.addEventListener('input',()=>{
  const q=sb.value.trim().toLowerCase();
  const allSec=document.getElementById('all-sections');
  const sr=document.getElementById('search-results');
  if(!q){
    sr.style.display='none'; allSec.style.display='';
    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-item')[0].classList.add('active');
    return;
  }
  allSec.style.display='none'; sr.style.display='';
  document.querySelectorAll('.nav-item').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));
  const hits=TOOL_DATA.filter(t=>
    t.name.toLowerCase().includes(q)||t.desc.toLowerCase().includes(q)||t.usage.toLowerCase().includes(q)
  );
  document.getElementById('search-count').textContent=`พบ ${hits.length} รายการ สำหรับ "${sb.value}"`;
  const hl=str=>str.replace(new RegExp(q.replace(/[.*+?^${}()|[\]\\]/g,'\\$&'),'gi'),m=>`<mark>${m}</mark>`);
  document.getElementById('search-list').innerHTML = hits.length===0
    ? '<div style="color:var(--muted);padding:20px">ไม่พบเครื่องมือที่ตรงกัน</div>'
    : hits.map(t=>`<div class="search-result-item tool-card">
        <div class="tool-card-top"><span class="tool-name">${hl(t.name)}</span>
        ${t.link?`<a class="tool-link" href="${t.link}" target="_blank">🔗 เปิด</a>`:''}</div>
        <div class="search-result-cat">📁 ${t.secTitle}</div>
        <div class="tool-desc">${hl(t.desc)}</div></div>`).join('');
});

const bt=document.getElementById('back-top');
window.addEventListener('scroll',()=>bt.classList.toggle('visible',window.scrollY>400));

document.addEventListener('keydown',e=>{
  if((e.ctrlKey||e.metaKey)&&e.key==='k'){e.preventDefault();sb.focus();sb.select();}
  if(e.key==='Escape'){sb.value='';sb.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));sb.blur();}
});

showSection('all');
</script>
</body>
</html>
